# /app/(site)/

All public-facing routes live here.
The (site) route group adds a shared layout (nav + footer)
without affecting the URL structure.

Built in Phase 2:
- layout.tsx        → shared nav + footer
- page.tsx          → homepage (/)
- [category]/
    page.tsx        → /kitchen, /bedroom, etc.
- products/
    [slug]/
      page.tsx      → /products/[slug]
- guides/
    page.tsx        → /guides
    [slug]/
      page.tsx      → /guides/[slug]
- loading.tsx       → skeleton loader (Phase 4)
- error.tsx         → error boundary (Phase 4)
